                     <interp inst="t18721028-733-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>, Stealing one purse, four postage labels, 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 13<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 9<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. in money, and two Prussian notes, and 3<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. of <persName id="t18721028-name-135" type="victimName">
